---
import { steps } from '../../data/steps';
---
<section class="py-16 md:py-30 bg-neutral-50/50 border-y border-neutral-100">
  <div class="max-w-content mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <span class="text-xs font-black text-accent-500 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] bg-accent-100 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-6 inline-block">Our Methodology</span>
      <h2 class="text-display-md text-primary-950 tracking-tighter">유통 근육을 기르는 <br/><span class="text-accent-500">4단계 실전 프로세스</span></h2>
      <p class="mt-8 text-body-lg text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">단순한 이론이 아닌, 현장에서 매출과 성과로 증명하는 단계별 유통 경험 프로그램입니다.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="relative mt-20">
      <!-- Desktop Connecting Line -->
      <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-0 w-full h-px border-t-2 border-dashed border-primary-200 -translate-y-1/2 hidden lg:block -z-0"></div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12 lg:gap-8 relative z-10">
        {steps.map((step, index) => (
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center group">
            <div class="relative mb-10">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-950 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-black shadow-xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500 z-10 relative">
                {index + 1}
              </div>
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-accent-500 rounded-full scale-110 blur-md opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-40 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-[32px] border border-neutral-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-2xl hover:border-transparent transition-all duration-500 flex flex-col h-full w-full">
              <div class="mb-6 flex justify-between items-center text-[10px] font-black tracking-widest uppercase text-accent-500">
                <span>Phase 0{index + 1}</span>
                <span class="bg-accent-100 px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-accent-700">{step.duration}</span>
              </div>
              
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-primary-950 tracking-tighter mb-2">{step.title}</h3>
              <p class="text-sm font-bold text-primary-600 mb-6">{step.subtitle}</p>
              
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-grow">
                {step.description}
              </p>
              
              <div class="mt-auto flex flex-wrap gap-2 justify-center">
                {step.outcomes.map(outcome => (
                  <span class="text-[11px] font-bold text-primary-950 bg-primary-100/50 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-lg">
                    {outcome}
                  </span>
                ))}
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-20 text-center">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 p-4 px-6 bg-primary-950 rounded-[20px] text-white shadow-2xl">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
        <span class="text-sm md:text-base font-bold">이 과정을 수료하면 대행사 없이도 독립적인 유통 판로를 개척할 수 있습니다.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
